{"tid":1132451,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"真正殺得死thanos只有一個方法","createTime":"2019-04-30T10:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T17:41:43.000Z","uid":72260,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"902d2228f107c3293db40a451b1a548af4081a50","tid":1132451,"uid":72260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:09:09.000Z","msg":"就係去伏米亞推佢落去換番粒soul stone上嚟<br />\n雖然IM用咗手套將佢同佢哋軍隊化灰<br />\n但係既然大家都可以用手套返嚟<br />\n代表thanos同佢啲軍隊一樣可以<br />\n唯有soul stone先係真正嘅inevitable<br />\n假設隊長擺番曬啲石去返以前嘅地方到<br />\n一樣有人可以做反AVG4嘅嘢攞返啲石 逆轉無限<br />\n我諗到嘅唯一解決方法係 <br />\n2024年嘅時候隊長唔係擺返啲石<br />\n係應該學thanos咁用啲石去摧毁啲石<br />\n咁先降低咗咁多粒石喺嗰個年代比人攞返嘅機會<br />\n<br />\n（喺多重時間線下，其實你大可以話番去AVG4啲英雄判斷嘅年份再之前去攞番啲石）<br />\n<br />\n但咁樣做已經避免咗咁多粒石最巧合岀現嘅年份"},{"pid":"68f4d20980f59487816485b07b59a9ccd48af0ab","tid":1132451,"uid":72260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:10:14.000Z","msg":"多謝大家用咗一分鐘睇我9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f1b28c8a07bd4a12c06a377578682df6312e97","tid":1132451,"uid":16061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:38:41.000Z","msg":"ok<br />\n但邊個人真心愛佢？"},{"pid":"2beaaa50b5b4c43848d9239013e50d7db468da39","tid":1132451,"uid":41270,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"24f1b28c8a07bd4a12c06a377578682df6312e97","tid":1132451,"uid":16061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:38:41.000Z","msg":"ok<br />\n但邊個人真心愛佢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:17:49.000Z","msg":"佢班𡃁"},{"pid":"9337dee8dca754f35705c8723b8d6e57eafd4b88","tid":1132451,"uid":2377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T16:13:53.000Z","msg":"Dr.strange開到門去果個位 一野推佢去門就咪搞撚掂"},{"pid":"42d81c01602b5bfbac14c1f83efc663ec2dac429","tid":1132451,"uid":134522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24f1b28c8a07bd4a12c06a377578682df6312e97","tid":1132451,"uid":16061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-